trans-unit.source: The [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_winforms](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] and [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)] technologies have two similar but different property models.
trans-unit.target: Den [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_winforms](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] och [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)] tekniker har två liknande egenskapen modeller.

trans-unit.source: *Property mapping* supports interoperation between the two architectures.
trans-unit.target: *Egenskapsmappning* stöder driftskompatibilitet mellan två arkitekturerna.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Windows Forms and WPF Property Mapping](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Integration.PropertyMap"> </xref> som mappar <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost"> </xref> egenskaper till egenskaper på den värdbaserade [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_winforms](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] kontroll.

trans-unit.source: Scales the hosted [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_winforms](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] control, and tracks the scale factor.
trans-unit.target: Skalas den värdbaserade [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_winforms](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] styra och spårar skalfaktor.

trans-unit.source: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winforms](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-winforms-md.md)] controls do not support scaling in the same way as [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)] elements.
trans-unit.target: [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winforms](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-winforms-md.md)]kontroller har inte stöd för skalning på samma sätt som [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)] element.

trans-unit.source: For example, scaling a [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winforms](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-winforms-md.md)] control from a factor of 1 to a factor of 0.5 and back to a factor of 1 does not, in general, recover the original size of the control.
trans-unit.target: Till exempel skalning en [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winforms](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-winforms-md.md)] kontroll från en faktor på 1 till faktorn 0,5 och tillbaka till en faktor på 1 i allmänhet inte, återställa den ursprungliga storleken på kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: When a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost> element receives a TAB command from the <xref:System.Windows.Interop.IKeyboardInputSink.TabInto%2A> method, the first eligible control in <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.Child%2A> receives focus.
trans-unit.target: När en <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost>element får FLIKEN kommandon från den <xref:System.Windows.Interop.IKeyboardInputSink.TabInto%2A>metoden den första kvalificerade styra i <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.Child%2A>får fokus.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.Child%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Interop.IKeyboardInputSink.TabInto%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost>

trans-unit.source: The first control is specified by the `request` parameter.
trans-unit.target: Den första kontrollen har angetts av den `request` parameter.

trans-unit.source: When `request` is <xref:System.Windows.Input.FocusNavigationDirection>, the behavior is similar to pressing the TAB key.
trans-unit.target: När `request` är <xref:System.Windows.Input.FocusNavigationDirection>, sätt att trycka på TABB-tangenten.</xref:System.Windows.Input.FocusNavigationDirection>

trans-unit.source: When `request` is <xref:System.Windows.Input.FocusNavigationDirection>, the behavior is similar to pressing SHIFT+TAB.
